The global E-Scooter/Moped and E-Motorcycle market can be segmented into various categories based on product types and speed ranges. E-Scooters can be classified based on their range capacity, with options available for short-range, medium-range, and long-range commutes. Mopeds are divided into conventional fuel-based models and modern electric variants. E-Motorcycles are categorized into low-speed models suitable for urban commuting and high-speed versions designed for longer distances and highway use.

